column5: Despite all the poop I've been disturbing, the pooch and I got out for a couple of hours to chase some cats. Nothing large, but they seemed to like my left over salties.    Darned fish thieving dog kept jumping in the water trying to grab the fish as I was reeling in. What a hoot
I like the chanel cats, but the mud cats.Yuck!Thats just me. Nice pics bruce
By any chance is yer dog called Buck???  JF
That fish is a little channel cat...isnt it?  It has a forked tail.
Yup, nice channel cat for sure. The bullhead's have rounded caudal fin.
Nice channel cats Bruce.... must of been fun hooking into them Those look real good for the frying pan.... perfect size Jacques
